[{"title":"将Hexo博客部署到Github上托管","date":"2021-04-29T07:06:04.000Z","path":"2021/04/29/将Hexo博客部署到Github上托管/","content":"<h2 id=\"总览\"><a href=\"#总览\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总览\"></a>总览</h2><blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><p>创建一个特定名称的仓库 =&gt; 将Hexo博客所需的文件部署到Github</p>\n</blockquote>\n<!-- more  -->\n<h2 id=\"详细流程\"><a href=\"#详细流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"详细流程\"></a>详细流程</h2><h3 id=\"在Github创建一个新的仓库，该仓库用来存放博客所需要的文件\"><a href=\"#在Github创建一个新的仓库，该仓库用来存放博客所需要的文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在Github创建一个新的仓库，该仓库用来存放博客所需要的文件\"></a>在Github创建一个新的仓库，该仓库用来存放博客所需要的文件</h3>\n<p>注：选择 Creat a new repository</p>\n\n<p>注：用户名为Username，则创建的新仓库的url必须为Username.github.io（原因：github可以为每个User生成一个仅且一个静态网页，即Username.github.io）</p>\n<h3 id=\"部署\"><a href=\"#部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署\"></a>部署</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd ~&#x2F;blog   #工作目录回到blog目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注：<br>hexo clean : 删除blog/public目录（blog/public目录下存放的是heox博客所需要的文件）<br>hexo g : 生成blog/public目录<br>hexo d : 会生成blog/.deploy_git目录，blog/.deploy_git存放的所有文件会部署（deploy）至你新建的Username.github.io仓库。最后，Github会根据你的Username.github.io仓库的文件来自动生成Username.github.io网址的布局</p>\n<p>最后，至此，Hexo博客的部署已经完成。后续会介绍Hexo的主题如何搭建，若有兴趣，请见：</p>\n","updated":"2021-04-29T13:14:45.918Z","comments":true,"categories":[{"name":"在Linux上搭建Hexo+Github个人博客","slug":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linux%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"},{"name":"4.Hexo博客部署到Github","slug":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客/4-Hexo博客部署到Github","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linux%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/4-Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0Github/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo博客部署到Github","slug":"Hexo博客部署到Github","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/tags/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0Github/"}]},{"title":"使用Hexo搭建个人博客","date":"2021-04-29T04:28:48.000Z","path":"2021/04/29/使用Hexo搭建个人博客/","content":"<h2 id=\"流程总览\"><a href=\"#流程总览\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"流程总览\"></a>流程总览</h2><blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><p>mkdir ~/blog =&gt; cd ~/blog =&gt;hexo init =&gt; hexo g =&gt; hexo s =&gt; 完成</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"详细流程\"><a href=\"#详细流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"详细流程\"></a>详细流程</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir ~&#x2F;blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注:在家目录创建blog目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd ~&#x2F;blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注：进入blog目录，所有的Hexo博客相关文件都在blog目录中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注：因为没有路径，所以选择工作目录进行hexo init；该命令进行了hexo博客的初始化，在blog目录创建了一系列的所需文件以及目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注：在blog/public/里生成Hexo博客所需的静态文件（若没有public目录，则创建一个）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注：将blog/public/中这些博客所需的文件部署到localhost:4000/内网,你可以在浏览器输入localhost:4000看到hexo博客效果</p>\n<p>总结：上面的步骤成功地使用hexo来搭建出个人博客，并且通过hexo s来将blog/public/的所有文件部署到localhost:4000内网。后续将会介绍如何把blog/public/的文件一键部署到Github上而不是部署到server（即localhost:4000）上</p>\n","updated":"2021-04-29T12:53:14.146Z","comments":true,"categories":[{"name":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","slug":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linux%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"},{"name":"3.Hexo搭建个人博客","slug":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客/3-Hexo搭建个人博客","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linux%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/3-Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo搭建博客","slug":"Hexo搭建博客","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/tags/Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"}]},{"title":"Git的下载与配置","date":"2021-04-29T04:03:29.000Z","path":"2021/04/29/Git的下载与配置/","content":"<blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><p>配置Git的原因：是Hexo部署到Github的前提</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Git的安装\"><a href=\"#Git的安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Git的安装\"></a>Git的安装</h2><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3MN_du8Q7dUb8Rm_k7wb6g\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Linux上Git的安装</a>\n<h2 id=\"Git的配置\"><a href=\"#Git的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Git的配置\"></a>Git的配置</h2><p>前提：有一个Github账号<br>然后</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.name &quot;这里填写你的Github用户名&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">git config --global user.email &quot;这里填写你的Github的email&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后，你可以使用下面的命令查看配置是否成功</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git config --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>总结：上述步骤把（Hexo博客托管到Github的前提：Git）Git安装与配置执行完毕，接下来就可以把你的blog目录里面的文件放在Github上托管了</p>\n","updated":"2021-04-29T12:48:53.428Z","comments":true,"categories":[{"name":"在Linuxs上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","slug":"在Linuxs上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linuxs%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"},{"name":"2.(Hexo博客托管到Github的前提)Git的下载与配置","slug":"在Linuxs上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客/2-Hexo博客托管到Github的前提-Git的下载与配置","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linuxs%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/2-Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%89%98%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0Github%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90-Git%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E4%B8%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux上安装Git","slug":"Linux上安装Git","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/tags/Linux%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Git/"}]},{"title":"Hexo的搭建","date":"2021-04-28T08:51:21.000Z","path":"2021/04/28/Hexo的搭建/","content":"<blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><h2 id=\"总览：\"><a href=\"#总览：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总览：\"></a>总览：</h2><hr>\n<p>下载Nodejs =&gt; 下载cnpm =&gt; 下载Hexo<br>注解：<br>Nodejs: JSP的运行环境</p>\n<ul>\n<li>node: 让JSP运行在服务器的平台</li>\n<li>npm: JSP运行时Nodejs的默认程序包管理器<br>cnpm: 中国版的npm，本质与npm一样（npm：官方的包管理器 cnpm：中国版的。考虑到中国境内npm不够快，选择使用cnpm）<br>Hexo: 博客框架（使用Markdown解析文章），生成静态网页</li>\n<li><hr>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"详细流程\"><a href=\"#详细流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"详细流程\"></a>详细流程</h2><h3 id=\"下载Nodejs、配置Nodejs以及下载cnpm\"><a href=\"#下载Nodejs、配置Nodejs以及下载cnpm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载Nodejs、配置Nodejs以及下载cnpm\"></a>下载Nodejs、配置Nodejs以及下载cnpm</h3><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/21e42cd362e7\" title=\"\" target=\"\">nodejs的安装与配置以及cnpm的下载</a>\n<p>注：Nodejs、cnpm下载配置后使用 Nodejs的node -v、npm -v.cnpm的cnpm -v来查看是否下载成功</p>\n<h3 id=\"使用cnpm下载Hexo\"><a href=\"#使用cnpm下载Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用cnpm下载Hexo\"></a>使用cnpm下载Hexo</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注：Hexo下载后使用hexo -v来查看是否下载成功（若hexo -v后，出现command找不到的问题，可以把hexo软链接到/usr/local/bin/（就像上面的node、npm的软链接一样）eg: ln -s /usr/sbin/nodejs/bin/hexo /usr/local/bin/）</p>\n<p>总结：上述步骤将Hexo下载完成，后续会使用Hexo来搭建个人博客</p>\n","updated":"2021-04-29T12:36:02.267Z","comments":true,"categories":[{"name":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","slug":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linux%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"},{"name":"1.Hexo的下载","slug":"在Linux上搭建Hexo-Github个人博客/1-Hexo的下载","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%9C%A8Linux%E4%B8%8A%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAHexo-Github%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/1-Hexo%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/tags/Hexo/"}]},{"title":"序言","date":"2021-04-28T07:52:59.000Z","path":"2021/04/28/序言/","content":"<blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><p>之前看到的一句话：“Hacker是黑客，理想是网络资源共享，信息自由化”<br>              “Cracker是骇客，是以进行网络攻击取乐或获利的人”<br>              “So be a Hacker.Don’t be a cracker.”</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><p>做一个分享者、开源者，为后来的人提供一些便利。若能帮到一些人，那就更好。<br>路漫漫其修远兮，吾将上下而求索…<br>自己永在路上…</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>这是本人在Linux上利用Hexo+Github搭建的博客，是属于的自己的博客。在开始的时候，我觉得很难。现在看来，虽然每一步不是全部搞懂，但也有所了解。<br>很感谢网上的信息与资源，若无他人的指导，我想个人博客不可能搭建出来（虽然现在很多功能欠缺）。再次感谢他人的帮助！！</p>\n","updated":"2021-04-28T08:41:19.057Z","comments":true,"categories":[{"name":"序言","slug":"序言","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/categories/%E5%BA%8F%E8%A8%80/"}],"tags":[{"name":"序言","slug":"序言","permalink":"https://prvyx.github.io/tags/%E5%BA%8F%E8%A8%80/"}]},{"title":"Hello World","date":"2021-04-26T07:31:33.785Z","path":"2021/04/26/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","updated":"2021-04-26T07:31:33.785Z","comments":true,"categories":[],"tags":[]}]